<div class="confirmation-slip col-xs-10 col-xs-offset-1 col-sm-8 col-sm-offset-2">
      <div class="row">
      	<br>
      	<br>
        <h3 class="center-align">AEGIS 2017</h3>
        <h3 class="center-align">YEARBOOK PHOTO SHOOT</h3>
        <h3 class="center-align">CONFIRMATION SLIP</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
      	<br>
      	<br>
        <h4>This confirmation slip stands as proof that I, <span class="text-bold"><%= current_account.name %></span>, <span class="text-bold"><%=current_account.student_id %></span>, of <span class="text-bold"><%= current_account.yr.to_s + " ".html_safe + current_account.course%></span> agree to all the terms and conditions that have been laid out by the AEGIS 2016 Editorial Board in the AEGIS 2016 Photoshoot Primer. I have fully read and understood the primer and am aware of the possible consequences I must face should I break any of the terms and conditions listed.</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="row">
        <h4>This slip also confirms that I have signed up on <span class="text-bold"><%=@timeslot.date.strftime("%A, %B %d, %Y")%> at <%= @timeslot.start_time.to_s + " - " + @timeslot.end_time.to_s%></span>.</h4>
      </div>
      <div class="row lines">
      	<div class="col-xs-5 forms">
      		<h6 class="center-align">Signature of Student over Printed Name</h6>
      	</div>
      	<div class="col-xs-5 col-xs-offset-2 forms">
      		<h6 class="center-align">Date</h6>
      	</div>
      </div>
    </div>